        <h1>Etyllica</h1>
        <p>A 2D Game Engine in pure Java.</p>

        <p class="view"><a href="https://github.com/yuripourre/etyllica">View the Project on GitHub <small>yuripourre/etyllica</small></a></p>


        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/yuripourre/etyllica/zipball/master">Download <strong>ZIP File</strong></a></li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/yuripourre/etyllica/tarball/master">Download <strong>TAR Ball</strong></a></li>
